Create a new Class:
	package --> right click --> new --> Class (name with uppercase initial)	
	
Create a file in Eclipse 
	package --> right click --> New --> Other --> General --> File --> Next --> input file name
	
Check a Method Details:
	Command + Mouse over method name --> open declaration --> String.class
	
Constructor:
	Right click --> Source --> Generate Constructors using Fields
	
Getters && Setters:
	Right click --> Source --> Generate Getters and Setters...
	
toString
	Right click --> Source --> Generate toString()...
	 
	
	
Refresh:
	The project name --> right click --> refresh, then we can see the created new files
	

Formatter:
	Preferences --> Java --> Code Style --> Formatter